channel.title: How to hack a library computer!
channel.description:
I dunno about you, but MY library has computers that only let you search their library--no url bar, etc.! Here are a few tricks:
LEFT-click on the IE icon ONCE and then press F2. YOU CAN CHANGE IE'S NAME! Open the directory searcher, go to view>explorer bar>search bar. Then,Type in a url. A new menu is created. Click "Go directly to a URL" and then type in your URL! FREE INTERNET ACCESS TO WEBSITES!
Wanna run REGEDIT on that computer? COOL! This MAY work(untested) Ok, open the search bar, click "look for files and folders" type in the name "regedit" for the file name, search, and double-click regedit. IT MAY NOT WORK!
